{"tid":2719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本居酒屋屌柒某日本達人淨飲打卡掉垃圾","createTime":"2016-11-26T01:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T07:43:45.000Z","uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd4c0f4371be7eab69a2ad32e0a86701552eae1","tid":2719,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"香港人の恥が来店。 <br />\n１１月２３日に <br />\n当店に何度かいらしてくださった香港のお客様の友人を名乗り、 <br />\n「Kenshin Himura Cheung」という名で９時半に予約して <br />\n二人で来店。 <br />\n酒の注文の前に山ほど写真を撮る。 <br />\n酒は一杯づつのみで二時間弱の滞在。 <br />\nあとは、延々とおしゃべりと店の中の写真を撮るだけ。 <br />\n酒を楽しむのではなく、店に来たということの証拠を残したいだけ。 <br />\nスタンプラリーのつもりで店に来ているのか。 <br />\nそして、途中で買ってきて食いながら来たのであろうゴミをカウンターの上に残して帰る。 <br />\n<br />\nこれって、お土産？ <br />\n<br />\nまさに香港人の恥 <br />\n<br />\nシオシオ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－ <br />\n<br />\n內容大意： <br />\n<br />\n某個著名日本達人「劍心」走去日本居酒屋淨飲唔買野食，重要賴低Ｄ垃圾等人清理 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5069a5d13196c75fbd6410e8b08e11917bbad786","tid":2719,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:34:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/saketamanegiya/photos/a.406823286096215.1073741825.179530415492171/1001464603298744/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsaketamanegiya%2Fphotos%2Fa.406823286096215.1073741825.179530415492171%2F1001464603298744%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=sCdFQRGDBylZsrJLvB35p8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=89a7daba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/saketamanegiya/photos/a.406823286096215.1073741825.179530415492171/1001464603298744/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"3de211215f9cb3fe300b1c752220459af21e2ea7","tid":2719,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"港博客賴死唔走遺垃圾　日居酒屋斥港人之恥<br />\n<br />\n日本東京一間居酒屋今日於facebook點名批評一名來自香港的客人，指他與友人於周三(23日)到店舖光顧，但只叫了一杯酒，就在店內漫談，「賴死唔走」之餘更留低垃圾。居酒屋炮轟他是「香港人之恥」，事件引來網民熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n該居酒屋位於新宿區，貼文中指一名香港熟客的朋友早前以「Kenshin Himura Cheung」名義預約座位，並於前日帶另一位朋友光顧。有指該名香港客於落單前不停拍照，逗留了近2個小時，卻只是叫了一杯酒，期間亦不停拍攝店內的情況。居酒屋方面認為兩人並非享受飲酒，只是想拍照留下曾經光顧的證據。<br />\n<br />\n居酒屋其後又狠批對方遺下垃圾，並謂「這是禮物嗎？這是香港人的恥辱」，斥責該香港客是「冒牌美食家」及蠢材。有指該名香港客常到日本旅遊，於網絡界薄有名氣，而他於自己的facebook帳戶上亦自稱是「SSI國際唎酒師」，並擁有和食檢定資格。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161125/bkn-20161125194145556-1125_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161125%2Fbkn-20161125194145556-1125_00822_001.html&d=sCdFQRGDBylZsrJLvB35p8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=56b843fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161125/bkn-20161125194145556-1125_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"69c49f8d8142ff2b2f602c0f545102bb3ae943c4","tid":2719,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:38:12.000Z","msg":"影衰港人，屌哂佢哋老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af514ea2b889313d51f575bab99696d7cad097b2","tid":2719,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"肯定係因為無冰水啦 <br />\n劍心可？"},{"pid":"3e9ce9b343c8899b9aa6fdc7f54e5e704d07c1cb","tid":2719,"uid":2651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7aaa3d77d25178964a7a29d159d92d52ee4e2a","tid":271